{"tid":529564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發現香港出左個不得了嘅新晉科幻小說家","createTime":"2018-01-15T01:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T06:24:39.000Z","uid":28938,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2628caf2debe5bd87e0c981892102b0794691ab1","tid":529564,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T01:45:05.000Z","msg":"尋日無聊係App Store搵到個科幻小說apps，睇左幾個故仔真係不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n故事背景係香港，講一個叫衛斯理，受過嚴格中國人武術訓練既人點樣遇到一個又一個奇怪既故事，當中涉及外星文化、各國秘密組織，每個故事都好曲折離奇。<br />\n<br />\n睇左大約二十部故仔，最鐘意藍血人、大廈<br />\n<br />\n強烈向各位巴打推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ；btw 如果呢位新作家出書我實買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d23d0f4d5f5675a585d76f076c45989cfd305ad","tid":529564,"uid":158660,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T01:45:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0169d89b3c470aa922fb0d5025881294295a689","tid":529564,"uid":5375,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T01:49:10.000Z","msg":"我都有睇過，早排朋友介紹我睇既，頭兩集都正正常常，跟住無啦啦有外星人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果tvb翻拍做電視劇就好喇，題材幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d139a5c13b83c6f5d6c939874a1f73110ea9d79","tid":529564,"uid":14566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a0169d89b3c470aa922fb0d5025881294295a689","tid":529564,"uid":5375,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T01:49:10.000Z","msg":"我都有睇過，早排朋友介紹我睇既，頭兩集都正正常常，跟住無啦啦有外星人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果tvb翻拍做電視劇就好喇，題材幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T02:01:58.000Z","msg":"如果蒙嘉慧做女主角應該幾正"},{"pid":"ddb7c69d958c48c7b87da2a23cd343fba68768e3","tid":529564,"uid":28938,"like"